Rowdy Wolf glared at Megatron. His yellow optics narrowed at him, and 
he bared a small section of his teeth at him. "I wanted to talk to 
you and only you. The Vok have a message for you. Stay on your guard. 
They are returning and they are not happy with you and your war. You 
are a poision that must be disolved."
